<figure id="og_1650470015643" contenteditable="false" data-ke-type="opengraph" data-ke-align="alignCenter" data-og-type="website" data-og-title="KRaft - Apache Kafka Without ZooKeeper" data-og-description="Apache Kafka Raft (KRaft) simplifies Kafka architecture by consolidating metadata into Kafka, removing the ZooKeeper dependency. Learn how it works, benefits, and what this means for Kafka's scalability." data-og-host="developer.confluent.io" data-og-source-url="https://developer.confluent.io/learn/kraft/" data-og-url="https://developer.confluent.io/learn/kraft/" data-og-image="https://scrap.kakaocdn.net/dn/eEYDk/hyN63tENQl/xYTIK17vWiyaCVvTEpZ3Q0/img.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500&amp;face=0_0_500_500,https://scrap.kakaocdn.net/dn/ETlJm/hyN60RgHXU/YCUCgTjixzR36yX5GIpc9K/img.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500&amp;face=0_0_500_500"><a href="https://developer.confluent.io/learn/kraft/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-source-url="https://developer.confluent.io/learn/kraft/">
<div class="og-image" style="background-image: url('https://scrap.kakaocdn.net/dn/eEYDk/hyN63tENQl/xYTIK17vWiyaCVvTEpZ3Q0/img.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500&amp;face=0_0_500_500,https://scrap.kakaocdn.net/dn/ETlJm/hyN60RgHXU/YCUCgTjixzR36yX5GIpc9K/img.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500&amp;face=0_0_500_500');">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="og-text">
<p class="og-title" data-ke-size="size16">KRaft - Apache Kafka Without ZooKeeper</p>
<p class="og-desc" data-ke-size="size16">Apache Kafka Raft (KRaft) simplifies Kafka architecture by consolidating metadata into Kafka, removing the ZooKeeper dependency. Learn how it works, benefits, and what this means for Kafka's scalability.</p>
